    "DisplayDescription": "Hockrow Agency \nCase File #BR83215\nLead Investigator: Arken Mallor\n\nCase Summary: \nClient hired the agency to look into the destruction of one of their ships near <EM4>Glaciem Ring Wreck Site</EM4>. They are claiming that the ship was destroyed by an ex-partner and need the blackbox to prove it.\n\nContract Investigator Actions:\nDispatch to <EM4>Glaciem Ring Wreck Site</EM4> and locate the derelict ship. Secure the area from any hostiles. Retrieve the blackbox and deliver it to <EM4>[Destination|Target|Address]</EM4>.\n\nAdditional Notes:\nWhoever destroyed the ship could still be in the area so be prepared for a fight, as such this has been flagged as a <EM4>combat mission</EM4>.",
